{
  "stem": "3653.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, sometimes yes and sometimes no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you see they take a rabbi with a tallis and tefilllin, and they kill them, so-- so sometimes you think is no God.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And most, I believe in my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I have bad times, you know, in sleep when I-- when I saw my father, I knew right away I'll be saved.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not in Chelm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in another camp, I made-- I made friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about probably 2-- 23 or 24, probably.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The age where you go in the army, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About two and a half months, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And then later came a German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said he wants 100 people, work people, shoemakers, tailors, [INAUDIBLE], carpenters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said I'm a carpenter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what are you going to lose?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going to live there another month.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you dead anyways.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "During the time that you were there, had other-- had other transports also come in?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "New transports?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My [INAUDIBLE] already 39,000.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Same camp, everybody lives for himself, you know, just to survive, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every morning.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "God forbid one runs away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he took a line with people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then one SS man with a stick, and he count 1, 2, 3, like this, with a stick.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were searching around, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they find them, they hung him up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hung them up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody has to go out and see he's hung.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Germans stood with a [INAUDIBLE] and you pick things, so then you can turn around the man who hangs on the rope.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you have to look right, God forbid you don't look.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
